&lt;p&gt;I used this data to see how winning particular statistical categories correlated to winning basketball games. I was looking for some insight into the importance of different the aspects of the game, and more importantly, how important they are &lt;i&gt;relative to one another&lt;/i&gt;. By aggregating the data over the entire 2016-2017 season, we get the following table:&lt;/p&gt;

